1-Create folder
2- create view, public,controller,modules, db folders and app.js
3- install command
  => npm init
  => npm i express
4- Create routes folder
=> create web.js file
5- web.js require in main file app.js
6- install npm i ejs command and use require this app.set('view engine','ejs') in app.js main file 
7-create a connect.js file in db folder and run npm i mongoose command 
8- connect public folder to link image and css folder app.use(express.static('public'))